WEBVTT

00:03.755 --> 00:05.995
E. R.

00:05.996 --> 00:07.202
Previously on E. R.

00:07.203 --> 00:09.201
I feel terrible about what's happened.

00:09.202 --> 00:12.509
Which part? Me being crippled
or you getting sued for malpractice?

00:12.510 --> 00:15.710
I took some Vicodin out of a patient's
prescription bottle and I swallowed them.

00:15.711 --> 00:18.922
- Did you successfully expel them?
- Yes.

00:18.957 --> 00:21.841
- You coming back to work soon?
- Next week, I hope.

00:21.842 --> 00:23.778
I heard you were doing
immune therapy.

00:23.979 --> 00:25.806
As soon as the tumor vaccine's ready.

00:25.807 --> 00:27.518
I'm sorry. I can't stay.

00:27.819 --> 00:30.206
- I'll send in a surgical resident.
- Where do you think you are going?

00:30.207 --> 00:32.858
- I'm sorry.
- Get your ass over here now!

00:32.859 --> 00:36.821
Look, I know that it's been tense between us
and I really don't mean it to be.

00:36.822 --> 00:39.917
In a few weeks we'll just be
friendly co-workers all over again.

00:39.918 --> 00:41.879
I'm not sure that's what I want.

